data.description: Built in a DH Horton new development in desirable Upper Deerfield Twp. This nicely decorated and adorned 4 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom home has an open layout, large living room and good sizable bedrooms with a 2 car garage.  The beautiful kitchen has an eat-in dining area with plenty of counter area, built-in microwave with upgraded vinyl plank style flooring, recessed lighting  and ceiling fans.  There are 3 walk-in closets, the laundry room is on the 2nd level along with  the HVAC room.  Upgraded steel front and back exterior security door. The roof has a 30 year warranty. Included is  a "Smart Home Feature".  The Qolsys panel is the central hub that talks to all the devices interior and exterior security of your smart home which bridges the entire suite of products with Bluetooth capability, Wi-Fi integration, Z-Wave access, and cellular connectivity. This house is in move-in ready with a balance of 10 year transferable builders warranty.  Sellers can close quickly on this Express Home providing quality at an affordable price. Seller has a survey on this newer home located in this great community in a great location.
